            {
                "type": "stat_block",
                "subtype": "equipment",
                "name": "Blazons of Shared Power (Greater)",
                "level": 11,
                "price": {
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "subtype": "price",
                    "text": "1,350 gp",
                    "value": 1350,
                    "currency": "gp"
                },
                "text": "A set of greater blazons of shared power also replicates property runes from the primary weapon, so long as the secondary weapon meets all the prerequisites for a given rune and isn't a specific weapon. The secondary weapon gains the benefits of those runes. All of its own runes are suppressed. When you invest the blazons, you can elect for them to transfer only fundamental runes, in which case they function as standard blazons of shared power .",
                "sources": [
